            <bug_when>2007-09-06 07:09:26 +0200</bug_when>
            <thetext>The toolbar with the Ext theme shows a lovely graduation of colour. However, if you change the toolbar size the graduation of colour isn&#39;t enlarged and an ugly repeat appears.

1. Open http://demo.qooxdoo.org/current/showcase/
2. Open &quot;Themes&quot; and select &quot;Ext&quot; theme
3. Select &quot;Menu and Toolbar&quot;
4. Choose &quot;Icons: 32 Pixel&quot;.

The toolbar now looks wrong.

Hugh</thetext>
