            <bug_when>2007-09-11 12:43:08 +0200</bug_when>
            <thetext>This is a theme issue. The problem is that the old layout system don&#39;t has a really good support for complex styles. I think we need to wait for 0.8 to really fix this. A workaround would maybe be to replace the current image with a one which is higher so that the background is not repeating.</thetext>
